Good morning,

I am excited to welcome Eric Seufert back for a Stratechery Interview about=
 the ongoing transformation in digital advertising.

Seufert is the creator of Mobile Dev Memo ( https://mobiledevmemo.com/ ) , =
where he writes about digital advertising; Seufert also invests ( https://w=
ww.businessinsider.com/pitch-deck-eric-seufert-launches-10-million-fund-her=
acles-capital-2022-5 ) in startups in the mobile space through his fund Her=
